        public ClientSession login​(java.lang.String email,
                           java.lang.String password,
                           java.lang.String type)
                    throws InvalidLoginException
        This method is the main login method and it will send the correct login to the right method below by the type given.
        Parameters:
        email - - the email of the user that want to login.
        password - - the password of the user that want to login.
        type - - the type of the user that want to login.
        Returns:
        'ClientSession' contains the correct service.
        Throws:
        InvalidLoginException - - in case the email, password or type are not a match.
